From ecfac56e962728a04f568ca98e12690984c7e52a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Fri, 10 Apr 2026 15:59:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 08/16] =?UTF-8?q?feat:=20integrar=20Sentry=20para=20monito?=
 =?UTF-8?q?rizaci=C3=B3n=20de=20errores=20en=20producci=C3=B3n?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Instalar @sentry/nextjs
- sentry.client.config.js: captura errores de cliente en producci├│n,
  ignora errores de red esperados (ResizeObserver, Network Error, etc.)
- sentry.server.config.js + sentry.edge.config.js: captura errores
  de servidor y edge runtime
- instrumentation.js: inicializa Sentry en arranque del servidor,
  elimina fallback NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY
- next.config.js: envuelto con withSentryConfig para source maps
  y configuraci├│n de build
- Captura con contexto (endpoint tag) en 4 rutas cr├¡ticas:
  analyze-food, admin-delete-user, generate-routine, admin-assistant
- .env.example: a├▒adidas variables NEXT_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN,
  SENTRY_ORG, SENTRY_PROJECT

https://claude.ai/code/session_01RxAUiBksDN6FokXtJKoUQC
